String::Super
--------

This allows you to compact a list of strings into a superstring that contains all the strings,
however is generally shorter than all substrings concatenated.

Pre-Requirements
----------------

On Debian:
$ apt-get install libdist-zilla-plugins-cjm-perl libdist-zilla-plugin-git-perl libdist-zilla-plugin-repository-perl libdist-zilla-plugin-podweaver-perl


Building
--------
$ dzil build
$ dzil install
